    "title": "Ibeveu Xauho.",
    "body": "One of the many lords of Pandemonium, Ibeveu Xauho has a splotchy red body with the wings of a moth and the head of a frog. It smells of brimstone. The air around it ripples with heat.\n\n<lightgrey>Max HP: 205     </lightgrey><lightgrey> Will: ++       </lightgrey><lightgrey>   AC: ++++ +   </lightgrey><lightgrey>  EV: ++        </lightgrey>                \n<lightgrey>    rF: +..     </lightgrey><lightgrey>   rC: ++.      </lightgrey><lightgrey>rPois: +        </lightgrey><lightgrey>rNeg: ∞         </lightgrey><lightgrey>rElec: +        </lightgrey>\n<lightgrey>Threat: High    </lightgrey><lightgrey>Class: Demonic  </lightgrey><lightgrey> Size: Large    </lightgrey><lightgrey> Int: Human     </lightgrey>\nSpeed: 130% (normally travels faster than you)\n\nYou have about 75% to hit with the fire staff of Defence by Offence and 75% to hit with your pseudopods.\nIt has about 60% to hit you.\n\nAttack  Max Damage  \nHit     25          \n\nIt is immune to torment; and resistant to steam and miasma.\nIt can see invisible.\nIt can fly.\nIt can open doors.\nSPELLSET_PLACEHOLDERTo read a description, press the key listed above. (AdB) indicates damage (the sum of A B-sided dice), (x%) indicates the chance to defeat your Will, and (y) indicates the spell range; shown in red if you are in range.",
